{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act19side", "eventName": "綠野幻夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DV-S-1", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "困心", "storyInfo": "斐爾迪南為多蘿西取來了洛肯水箱實驗中回收的資料，可她需要這些資料的理由，卻出乎斐爾迪南的意料。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g5_laboratory", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你想要的資料。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，斐爾迪南。沒想到你會親自來找我。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了你與政府部門斡旋，我們回收了洛肯水箱的大部分數據。這一點沒必要讓太多人知道。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......我想瞭解下你需要這部分資料的原因。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她靜靜地看著面前的顯示器，無比專注，甚至放輕了呼吸。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "螢幕上正在播放一段錄影，錄影的主角是一個白髮女孩。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大部分時間裡，女孩都在睡覺、進食，或者蜷縮在空房間裡發呆。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偶爾她會被領到實驗室裡，隔著一米多厚的隔離牆，將另一間實驗室裡的桌椅捏成廢鐵。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是個美麗的孩子。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的語氣讓我想起洛肯·威廉姆斯。我以為只有瘋子才會把受試者當成“傑作”到處炫耀。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，許多人譴責他突破了道德底線。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道德？那是庸人為了躲避風險而給自己套上的枷鎖。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "科學本就是超脫常識的。以道德為標準去評價一個科學家，對他而言是莫大的侮辱。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威廉姆斯最大的問題在於，他被眼前無窮無盡的未知逼瘋了，喪失了一個科學家應有的理性。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以看一眼最後那段錄影，看看這個你口中的“美麗的孩子”是怎麼把實驗室變成天災現場的——", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "螢幕上的畫面發生了變化。"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時的監控器並未錄下任何聲音，可此起彼伏的悲鳴依然穿透了螢幕，衝擊著數年之後的另一間實驗室。"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再多坍塌的磚石都掩蓋不掉那滿地的血色。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個孩子......她最後去哪了？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與她有關的資料有明顯的被篡改的痕跡。很顯然，就和洛肯水箱的全部遺產一樣，她對某些組織來說還有利用價值。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南，我想找到她。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我假定你並不是為了繼續威廉姆斯的實驗而去尋找這個受試者。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她太不可控了。萊茵生命無法承受如此巨大的風險。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她從來不是自願地走進實驗室。我不能提出這麼殘忍的要求。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你是想治癒她？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都不是醫生，但只要是看過了整個實驗過程的人，就不該再抱著這樣的妄想。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，斐爾迪南。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想找到她，然後......抱抱她。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱......抱她？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個孩子......她太孤獨了。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們奪去了她的家人，又將她變得與所有人都不一樣。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忍不住想......她現在在哪裡？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她有沒有認識新朋友，會不會遇上新的敵人？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好想聽聽她的聲音......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我改變不了她的過去，但我希望她至少還能擁有未來。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西，你知道嗎？你時常讓我感到......捉摸不透。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像你這樣感情用事的科學家很少見。理性同樣無法約束你，說不定哪一天，你會變得比威廉姆斯更加瘋狂。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......瘋狂嗎？我曾無數次在夢中見過類似的情形。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是我很想找到這個孩子的原因。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是她還活著......要是有人能從這麼悲慘的過去中拯救她......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼我相信，假如有一天我當真瘋了，也一定會有人來阻止我。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}